;; A reusable definition partial (§15.9). Forms include it with
;; {:include :contact-note}; it is spliced in when the form is served, so a fix
;; here reaches every form that includes it.
{:id :contact-note
 :partial [:c/paragraph {:text "Tip: this note is a reusable partial — defined once in partials/, spliced into any form that includes it."}]}
